
# Rasa Secretary Chatbot

A simple Rasa chatbot that can answer frequently asked questions about CSD, provide contact information for a teacher by surname, and use ChatGPT API to answer out-of-scope questions. 

## Prerequests

Install python and check python version

```bash
  python --version
```

Install virtual environment

```bash
  python -m virtualenv venv
```

Activate virtual environment

```bash
  venv\Scripts\activate
```
Install Rasa

```bash
  pip rasa install
```

Check Rasa installation 

```bash
  rasa --version
```

## Run Locally

Clone the project

```bash
  git clone https://github.com/Kaivanov21/RasaChatbot
```

Go to the project directory

```bash
  cd RasaChatbot
```

Run action server

```bash
  rasa run actions
```

Intercat with chatbot via command line

```bash
  rasa shell
```
Start rasa server (intercat with chatbot via website widget)

```bash
  rasa run -m models --enable-api --cors “*”
```

## Useful commands

Train rasa model

```bash
  rasa train
```

Interact with chatbot via command line and to see what model extracts as intents and entities from text

```bash
  rasa shell nlu
```

Interactive learning session with chatbot via command line

```bash
  rasa interactive
```

Build and run images with Docker Compose

```bash
  docker-compose up --build
```
  
